  "title": "Product Manager (Telecom, International Connectivity)",
  "description": "<p><strong>about company </strong></p>\n<p>I am currently working with a well-known telecommunications company in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Permanent role. Salary structure: Base + Bonus. 5 days in office. 2 rounds of interview to offer.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>about job (please reach out for more detailed JD)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Take responsibility for the product line's performance and profitability; related to international connectivity business</li>\n  <li>Manage the product cost structure and define the pricing strategy.</li>\n  <li>Manage and optimize the commercial model and cost structure with customers and partners.</li>\n  <li>Develop business cases, models, and analysis to support new product development and customization.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>skills and requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min 5 years of experience in Product Management, Product Marketing, or Business Development</li>\n  <li>Has background in Telecommunication industry</li>\n  <li>Possess strong financial, data mining, and analysis skills</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of the telecom business.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To apply online please use the 'apply' function, alternatively you may contact Stella at 96554170 (EA: 94C3609 /R1875382)</p>",
